OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FWords by ITV News' Senior Producer/
OL,7,FDirector, Tim Maynard
OL,9,FIt was a plot that investigators
OL,10,Fbelieve could have killed more people
OL,11,Fthan 9/11.
OL,13,FTwenty years after British authorities
OL,14,Funcovered a terrorist plan to smuggle
OL,15,Fliquid explosives onto transatlantic
OL,16,Fairliners and destroy multiple
OL,17,Fpassenger jets bound for North
OL,18,FAmerica, the spies, police officers
OL,19,Fand intelligence officials at the
OL,20,Fheart of the operation are revealing
OL,21,Fhow disaster was narrowly avoided.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
