PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FHidden inside an East London flat, MI5
OL,7,Fsurveillance equipment allowed
OL,8,Fofficers to watch preparations unfold
OL,9,Fin real time.
OL,11,FFormer investigators describe the
OL,12,Fmoment they realised they were dealing
OL,13,Fwith an active plot moving ever closer
OL,14,Ftowards execution.
OL,16,FThat sense of a threat moving closer
OL,17,Falso reached the heart of government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FJohn Reid, the then home secretary,
OL,7,Fwas under immense pressure from civil
OL,8,Fservants to raise the threat level to
OL,9,Faviation and warn the public.
OL,11,FBut MI5 feared that doing so would
OL,12,Falert the plotters that the security
OL,13,Fservices were on to them `
OL,14,Fcompromising the covert operation at
OL,15,Fthe moment it mattered most.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FIn discussions with Jonathan Evans,
OL,7,Fthe then MI5 deputy director, Reid had
OL,8,Fto balance the duty to protect the
OL,9,Fpublic with the need to keep the
OL,10,Fplotters unaware until police were
OL,11,Fready to move.
OL,13,FAs Reid recalls, had they got it
OL,14,Fwrong, "there would have been a
OL,15,Fterrible, tragic loss of life. The
OL,16,Fgovernment would've been in grave
OL,17,Fdanger of falling".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FThe documentary also reveals the
OL,7,Fextraordinary cooperation ` and
OL,8,Foccasional tension ` between Britain
OL,9,Fand the US.
OL,11,FIn Washington, intelligence from the
OL,12,Finvestigation was shared at the
OL,13,Fhighest levels of government.
OL,15,FFormer US National Security Advisor
OL,16,FJuan Zarate recalls White House
OL,17,Fdiscussions about whether the
OL,18,Fconspirators were "on the brink" and
OL,19,Fconcerns that authorities might "wait
OL,20,Ftoo long".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FMeanwhile, former CIA senior analyst
OL,7,FWayne McCool describes how American
OL,8,Fspecialists tested versions of the
OL,9,Fbomb designs being assembled by the
OL,10,Fplotters.
OL,12,FThe result, he says, was unequivocal:
OL,13,F"They worked as designed. They went
OL,14,Fboom."
OL,16,FEventually, events moved at
OL,17,Fextraordinary speed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FAfter intelligence led to the arrest
OL,7,Fof Rashid Rauf in Pakistan, security
OL,8,Fservices feared the conspirators in
OL,9,FBritain could be triggered into early
OL,10,Faction.
OL,12,FHundreds of officers were mobilised,
OL,13,Fand suspects were arrested across the
OL,14,Fcountry in coordinated overnight raids
OL,15,Fin east London, High Wycombe and
OL,16,FBirmingham.
OL,18,FFormer police officers and
OL,19,Fintelligence staff describe a frantic
OL,20,Foperation as names were ticked off one
OL,21,Fby one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FThe arrests prevented the plot from
OL,7,Fprogressing further, but the impact
OL,8,Fwas immediate.
OL,10,FAirports across Britain were thrown
OL,11,Finto chaos as emergency security
OL,12,Fmeasures were introduced.
OL,14,FThousands of flights were cancelled,
OL,15,Fpassengers stranded and stringent
OL,16,Frestrictions imposed on what
OL,17,Ftravellers could carry onboard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FMany of those changes, including
OL,7,Flimits on liquids in hand luggage,
OL,8,Fremain familiar to passengers two
OL,9,Fdecades later.
OL,11,FThe subsequent investigation generated
OL,12,Fone of the largest bodies of evidence
OL,13,Fassembled in a British terrorism case.
OL,15,FAlthough the plotters had not yet
OL,16,Fpurchased airline tickets and their
OL,17,Fdevices were not yet viable,
OL,18,Fprosecutors argued the conspiracy was
OL,19,Freal, advanced and moving towards
OL,20,Fexecution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FFollowing a series of trials, Abdulla
OL,7,FAhmed Ali, Assad Sarwar and Tanvir
OL,8,FHussain were convicted for their roles
OL,9,Fin the plot to bomb transatlantic
OL,10,Fairliners.
OL,12,FFive other members of the network were
OL,13,Ffound guilty of conspiracy to murder,
OL,14,Fwhile two more were convicted of
OL,15,Fterrorism preparation offences.
OL,17,FAs for Rauf, American intelligence
OL,18,Fofficials believe that he was killed
OL,19,Fin a US drone strike in November 2008.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31419
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FThe Foreign, Commonwealth &
OL,7,FDevelopment Office declined to confirm
OL,8,Freports of his death.
OL,10,FUltimately, Terror in the Skies:
OL,11,FStopping the Liquid Bomb Plot is the
OL,12,Fstory of the people who prevented
OL,13,Fcatastrophe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
