PN,31420
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784911676
OL,3,CTerror in the Skies: The plot that
OL,4,Ccould have brought down the government
OL,6,FThrough exclusive interviews with MI5
OL,7,Fofficers, senior detectives, ministers
OL,8,Fand intelligence officials on both
OL,9,Fsides of the Atlantic, this ITV
OL,10,FExposure programme reveals how a vast
OL,11,Finternational operation disrupted a
OL,12,Fconspiracy that threatened thousands
OL,13,Fof lives.
OL,15,FTwenty years on, those who were there
OL,16,Fcan finally tell the story of how one
OL,17,Fof the most ambitious terror plots
OL,18,Fever uncovered was stopped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
